Q">Mộng Phương Phu Nhược kỳ 1 - 夢方孚若其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Trang/author-QKy6LHJMqAcMRcgSw6RXSA">Lưu Khắc Trang</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Ch%E1%BA%A9n/Th%C3%B9-L%E1%BA%A1c-Thi%C3%AAn-T%E1%BA%A7n-m%E1%BB%99ng-Vi-Chi/poem-Yb0CfRt_mpuB5Jvk-13RgA">Thù Lạc Thiên “Tần mộng Vi Chi” - 酬樂天頻夢微之</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Ch%E1%BA%A9n/author-bMSP5YOXWyK1jTzTI9MKNQ">Nguyên Chẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/T%E1%BB%91ng-%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Minh-Ph%E1%BB%A7/poem-78OH3D67o2G5gabxaBWAOQ">Tống Đỗ Minh Phủ - 送杜明府</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/%C6%AFu-l%C3%A3o/poem-qIyjHbe0mdIhfT_8koDJGA">Ưu lão - 憂老</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/author-5S8czaSOqXhHlNE7NtKr8g">Đặng Trần Côn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
